pan></h2></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-42 fusion-no-large-visibility fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"--awb-text-color:#202020;--awb-font-size:25px;\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Plus Jakarta Sans&quot;;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0;font-size:1em;letter-spacing:-0.015em;text-transform:var(--awb-typography1-text-transform);--fontSize:25;--minFontSize:25;line-height:1.5;text-shadow:0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What is Medical Tourism?</span></h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-27\" style=\"--awb-font-size:18px;--awb-line-height:1.72em;--awb-letter-spacing:var(--awb-typography4-letter-spacing);--awb-text-transform:var(--awb-typography4-text-transform);--awb-text-color:var(--awb-color8);--awb-margin-right:10px;--awb-margin-left:10px;--awb-text-font-family:&quot;Cardo&quot;;--awb-text-font-style:normal;--awb-text-font-weight:400;\"><p>International travel to receive medical care is known as Medical Tourism. It is also called health tourism, surgical tourism, international surgery tourism, or medical travel.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-25 fusion-flex-container nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-padding-right:20px;--awb-padding-left:20px;--awb-background-color:var(--awb-color1);--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap\" style=\"max-width:1310.4px;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-24 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:10px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:20px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-43 fusion-no-small-visibility fusion-no-medium-visibility fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"--awb-text-color:#202020;--awb-font-size:35px;\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Plus Jakarta Sans&quot;;font-style:normal;font-weight:300;margin:0;font-size:1em;letter-spacing:-0.015em;text-transform:var(--awb-typography1-text-transform);--fontSize:35;line-height:1.5;text-shadow:0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What is needed to start Medical Tourism Business?</span></h2></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-44 fusion-no-large-visibility fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"--awb-text-color:#202020;--awb-font-size:25px;\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Plus Jakarta Sans&quot;;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0;font-size:1em;letter-spacing:-0.015em;text-transform:var(--awb-typography1-text-transform);--fontSize:25;--minFontSize:25;line-height:1.5;text-shadow:0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What is needed to start Medical Tourism Business?</span></h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-28\" style=\"--awb-font-size:18px;--awb-line-height:1.72em;--awb-letter-spacing:var(--awb-typography4-letter-spacing);--awb-text-transform:var(--awb-typography4-text-transform);--awb-text-color:var(--awb-color8);--awb-margin-right:10px;--awb-margin-left:10px;--awb-text-font-family:&quot;Cardo&quot;;--awb-text-font-style:normal;--awb-text-font-weight:400;\"><p>International travel to receive medical care is known as Medical Tourism. It is also called health tourism, surgical tourism, international surgery tourism, or medical travel.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-29\"><ol>\n<li><strong>Research</strong> – You need to know the scope. You need to ensure that this business is for you or not. It would be best if you found out the pros and cons of this business, and for this purpose, you'll need to do market research. You can do it on your own using the internet or hire an expert.</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><strong>Create a Business Plan</strong> – You need to develop a business plan which will include financial planning, resource planning, what type of services you'll target, what countries you'll target, etc.</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><strong>Create a Team</strong> – A great team is necessary for the success of every business. The Medical Tourism business needs many critical and specialized roles like Surgeons, Doctors, Counselors, etc. You need to have identified people in every role.</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><strong>Get Certifications, Licenses, and Permits</strong> – Medical Tourism businesses have many legal requirements. Different countries have a different license and permit requirements. You need to take care of these legal requirements according to the requirement. There are many international certifications available that benefits you to stand out from your competitors.</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li><strong>IT Infrastructure (Software, Web App, Mobile Apps)</strong> – You'll need your client to connect with you from her home country. The client should be able to share all his reports, including MRI, CT Scan, Ultrasound, etc. For this purpose, you need to have a Web App that allows the clients to upload DICOM Files which the Surgeons/Doctors can see online using a DICOM Viewer. The Software also needs to support the patients before and after the surgery. For this purpose, the clients should be able to take care of pre-op and post-op requirements online. They should be able to fill out online surveys, which help the team to know the progress. For this purpose, you can plan to schedule a demo of Cure-o-Tour.</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li><strong>Promote your business</strong> – You must let the world know you exist. For this purpose, you need to promote your business, and mainly this promotion needs to be done digitally. Search Engine Optimization, Social Media Marketing, and Google Ads (PPC) are some ways to bring your business to your clients.</li>\n</ol>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-26 fusion-flex-container has-pattern-background has-mask-background nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap\" style=\"max-width:1310.4px;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-25 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:20px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-30\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:10px;\"><p>There are many experts available who can help you from the start to set up your Medical Tourism Business completely. We have identified one such expert on whom you can rely. Check their website at <a href=\"https://medicaltourismbusiness.com/\">https://medicaltourismbusiness.com/</a></p>\n<p>Note: The article provides general guidance on how to start a medical tourism business, and don't take it as final steps. Also, if you think I have missed any steps, please let me know by commenting on this article. Thanks.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div>\n","date":"2022-12-24T01:57:59","author":{"node":{"name":"Sanjay Kumar","avatar":{"url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12cd5109e81ca7f47c3bdfd017c1351234efe746c16d7811a74e031e6887c0e7?s=96&d=mm&r=g"}}},"featuredImage":{"node":{"altText":"","gatsbyImageData":null}}}},"pageContext":{"id":"cG9zdDoxMjA5NA=="}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{"footer":"footer","header":"header"}}